OL,4,Ctrust failed to monitor use of seating
OL,6,FThe investigation also found the trust
OL,7,Fdid not fully assess Harry's needs
OL,8,Fbefore approving the chairs, nor ask
OL,9,Fhis parents for consent on their use.
OL,11,F"Finally, after all these years, Harry
OL,12,Fis believed. This report is his voice,
OL,13,Fand it has always been about him",
OL,14,Fsaid Deirdre.
OL,16,FHarry can walk unaided and used a
OL,17,Fspecial chair at meal times.
