OL,6,F"So I think it is really important
OL,7,Fthat that our public services are
OL,8,Faware of the impact of their actions."
OL,10,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for the
OL,11,FWestern Trust said: "The trust will be
OL,12,Fcontacting the service user and their
OL,13,Ffamily to offer a sincere apology.
OL,15,F"We have accepted the findings and
OL,16,Flearning within the ombudsman's report
OL,17,Fand an action plan has been developed
OL,18,Fto take the recommendations and
OL,19,Flearning forward."
