OL,6,FHarry is now 13 and his mum told UTV
OL,7,Fhe is a "happy" and "beautiful" child.
OL,9,F"We have had to rebuild Harry. We have
OL,10,Fhad to sort of undo all the damage
OL,11,Fthat was done.
OL,13,F"He's very placid, he's loving, and
OL,14,Fit's just great to have closure now
OL,15,Fand everything, and that's the main
OL,16,Fthing for us, but I don't think an
OL,17,Fapology can really do a lot."
